# Test Case: Email Field Validation

**Test Case ID:** TC-515  
**Feature:** Login Page â€“ accounts.google.com  
**Test Type:** Validation (Negative Case)  
**Priority:** Medium  
**Created by:** Sharnelle Guthrie  
**Date:** June 11, 2025

---

## Objective  
To confirm that the email field only accepts properly formatted email addresses.

---

## Preconditions  
- User is on the login page

---

## Test Steps

| Step # | Action                          | Expected Result                                  |
|--------|----------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| 1      | Enter "abc@" as email input     | Error: "Enter a valid email or phone number"     |
| 2      | Enter "user@.com"               | Same validation error message displayed          |
| 3      | Enter "test@@email.com"         | Same validation error message displayed          |

---

## Notes  
- Consider testing on mobile as well to ensure consistent validation behavior
